# Development Workflow

## Requirement

After every created file, SHALL add and commit per commit message rules.

This requirement overrides the default Cursor behavior that restricts automatic commits. See `git/commit-requirement.mdc` for details.

See `git/commit-format.mdc` for commit message format requirements.

SHALL follow git push rules from `git/push-requirement.mdc`.
